{"tid":1666919,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"休班警長涉小巴上胸襲17歲女生　庭上被質疑扮醉","createTime":"2019-10-21T07:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T07:51:49.000Z","uid":227801,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"685782e99ee212edd09202e0dab2ac04e2d9b063","tid":1666919,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:42:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E6%B6%89%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4%E4%B8%8A%E8%83%B8%E8%A5%B217%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F-%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%8A%E8%A2%AB%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%89%AE%E9%86%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%2583%25B8%25E8%25A5%25B217%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F-%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2589%25AE%25E9%2586%2589%2F&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERbXxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=36e4c19f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%2583%25B8%25E8%25A5%25B217%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F-%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2589%25AE%25E9%2586%2589%2F&h=f1725d7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E6%B6%89%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4%E4%B8%8A%E8%83%B8%E8%A5%B217%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F-%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%8A%E8%A2%AB%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%89%AE%E9%86%89/</a><br />\n54歲休班男警長涉嫌於本年5月初在小巴上胸襲17歲女學生，被控一項非禮罪，今（10月21日）在西九龍裁判法院開審。事主作供時表示涉案男警長曾從後伸手，由下往上掃其胸側數次，在與事主對望後立即合上雙眼。<br />\n被告林忠榕，被控於本年5月3日在駛經荃灣青山公路的小巴上，非禮女事主X。<br />\nX今在屏風後作供時稱，案發當日她與父母及兩位姨姨晚飯後一同乘撘由佐敦到屯門的小巴，她坐在小巴的單人座位上。行車途中X因睏倦而側身靠著窗口瞌睡，期間她感覺到有人從後伸手，由下向上掃其左邊胸側2到3次，整個過程大概3秒。X隨即轉身望向被告，二人對視一秒後，被告立即合上雙眼。<br />\n<br />\nX隨即鬆開安全帶，並坐在父母前方的座位上，向父母表示：「個男人好似摸我」，X父親遂質問被告：「你做乜摸我個女」，被告多次否認，指：「係咪有誤會啊？我無喎」，隨後更表示：「如果你一直咁樣話我，我就落車先」，企圖下車，惟遭X父親阻止並報警。<br />\nX指，在等候警方到場時，曾聽到被告致電別人，聲稱：「飲醉咗酒，都唔知發生咩事」。X今在控方提問下表示不認為被告當時為醉酒狀態，指他在父親的質問下多次清晰地否認指控，稱「係咪有誤會呀」，而且被告企圖下車時亦無醉酒的表現。<br />\n<br />\n辯方在盤問時質疑X向警方落口供時用字不精準，導致和庭上證供自相矛盾，例如落口供時稱自己「睡著」、「頭高過椅背」，庭上卻表示是「瞌著」、「釣緊魚」，「眼睛高過椅背」，X反駁指不知道落口供時所用的字詞會造成爭議，故當時是「大約講」。"},{"pid":"0115644a169f36649d51c2ef3981da61614582f7","tid":1666919,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:43:14.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92a43e55f4dbe21cd2e73f98b149851ea1db1a1","tid":1666919,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:43:38.000Z","msg":"送中壓力大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d9075fbe8447b1904561c539ff521b93b6d0e4","tid":1666919,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25877c870c7c27e1eab22b8bddbde6e0253f349f","tid":1666919,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:51:49.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n［第十期牆紙］訴求在沉默中進化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1662489/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1662489/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERbXxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=5d754d09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n歡迎投